title: The Nearly Complete Dubliners - Irish Drinking Songs
description:
The main problem with The Dubliners ? the quintessential classic Irish Pub Band for over 40 years ? is that they have released the same tracks on about 35 different albums. This makes constructing a discography a mix between difficult and pointless, considering that if you have three of their albums, you really have about 15 of them. Add to that the fact that getting their torrents properly seeded has proven difficult, and it becomes a pain in the ass to try to get all their stuff. What I present here is just about every classic song they have produced (and a couple of different covers of the same ones) released in one torrent. I cannot call this the ?complete? Dubliners, but it?s pretty damned close. If anyone out there has anything I?m missing, especially the LIVE albums, please torrent them up and link to this one. Also, so nobody else has to go through the 4 months it took me to get this far with over 20 different torrent sites, please keep this thing seeded. I will keep it available for the next six months, at least.
